"font-size:\r\n      12.0pt;font-family:宋体;color:black\">28</span></p>\r\n      </td>\r\n    </tr>\r\n  </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<p style=\"margin-right:0cm;margin-left:0cm;font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\'Calibri\',\'sans-serif\';margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:30.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;color:#333333\">有意愿参与本次市场调研的设备生产企业、经营企业请于<span>2022</span>年<span>02</span>月 <span>22</span>日前将相关材料发送至邮箱：</span><span><a href=\"mailto:ycyysbc@qq.com。\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">ycyysbc@qq.com</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span>。</span></span></a></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-right:0cm;margin-left:0cm;font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\'Calibri\',\'sans-serif\';margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:30.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;color:#333333\">现场咨询会时间另行通知。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-right:0cm;margin-left:0cm;font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\'Calibri\',\'sans-serif\';margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-indent:24.1pt;line-height:30.0pt\"><strong><span style=\"font-family:宋体;color:#333333\">报名须知：</span></strong></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-right:0cm;margin-left:0cm;font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\'Calibri\',\'sans-serif\';margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:30.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;color:#333333\">1.</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;color:#333333\">具有独立承担民事责任的能力。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-right:0cm;margin-left:0cm;font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\'Calibri\',\'sans-serif\';margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:30.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;color:#333333\">2.</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;color:#333333\">具有履行合同所必须具备的设备和专业知识。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-right:0cm;margin-left:0cm;font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\'Calibri\',\'sans-serif\';margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:30.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;color:#333333\">3.</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;color:#333333\">具有良好的商业信誉。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-right:0cm;margin-left:0cm;font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\'Calibri\',\'sans-serif\';margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:30.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;color:#333333\">4.</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;color:#333333\">近<span>3</span>年内在经营活动中无严重不良记录。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-right:0cm;margin-left:0cm;font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\'Calibri\',\'sans-serif\';margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:30.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;color:#333333\">5.</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;color:#333333\">按要求填写《盐城市第一人民医院设备咨询报名表》（见附件）。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-right:0cm;margin-left:0cm;font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\'Calibri\',\'sans-serif\';margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:30.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;color:#333333\">6.</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;color:#333333\">报名截止时间：<span>2022</span>年<span>02</span>月<span>21</span>日<span>24</span>：<span>00</span></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-right:0cm;margin-left:0cm;font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\'Calibri\',\'sans-serif\';margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:30.0pt\"><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt;\">联系人：李老师</span><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt;\">&nbsp; </span><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt;\">联系方式：</span><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt;\">0515-88508946&nbsp; QQ:651830413(</span><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt;\">推荐</span><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt;\">)</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-right:0cm;margin-left:0cm;font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\'Calibri\',\'sans-serif\';margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:30.0pt\"><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt;\"><br>\r\n</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-right:0cm;margin-left:0cm;font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\'Calibri\',\'sans-serif\';margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:30.0pt\"><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt;\">附件：<img border=\"0\" src=\"/ewebeditor/sysimage/icon16/doc.gif\"><a href=\"/ewebeditor/uploadfile/file/2022/02/14/20220214144937669.docx\" target=\"_blank\">设备咨询报名表.docx</a></span></p>','','','','','');
INSERT INTO `p8_cms_item_article_addon` VALUES ('2381','3204','1','','','依据国务院《关于印发《发热门诊设置管理规范》《新冠肺炎定点救治医院设置管理规范》的通知》联防联控机制医疗发【2021】80号文件及上级部门的要求，盐城市儿童医院须设置新冠肺炎救治发热门诊。经医院党委研究决定，发热门诊需要采购专用方舱CT一台，充分做好新冠肺炎','172.16.100.2','172.16.100.2','1644821545','<p style=\"margin-right:0cm;margin-left:0cm;font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\'Calibri\',\'sans-serif\';margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:10.0pt;margin-left:0cm;layout-grid-mode:char;font-size:11.0pt;font-family:\'Tahoma\',\'sans-serif\';text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:2\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:2;font-family:宋体\">依据</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:2;font-family:宋体\">国务院《关于印发《发热门诊设置管理规范》《新冠肺炎定点救治医院设置管理规范》的通知》联防联控机制医疗发【<span>2021</span>】<span>80</span>号</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:2;font-family:宋体\">文件及上级部门的要求，盐城市儿童医院须设置新冠肺炎救治发热门诊。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-right:0cm;margin-left:0cm;font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\'Calibri\',\'sans-serif\';margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:2\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">经医院党委研究决定，发热门诊需要采购专用方舱<span>CT</span>一台，充分做好新冠肺炎的救治准备。并按照</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">盐财购【<span>2020</span>】<span>1</span>号市财政局《关于转发《财政部办公厅关于疫情防控采购便利化的通知》的通知》的要求；我院对本次项目的采购申请按照快捷流程进行招标。</span></p>','','','','','');
INSERT INTO `p8_cms_item_article_addon` VALUES ('2382','3205','1','','/ewebeditor/uploadfile/image/2022/02/16/20220216110050997001.jpg','在传统的元宵佳节来临之际，为营造欢乐祥和的节日气氛，进一步丰富老同志的精神文化生活，2022年2月14日，盐城市第一人民医院离退休干部处举办了“迎元宵 猜灯谜”活动，吸引了不少老同志前来参与。活动现场张灯结彩，200多条挂在彩带上的谜面随风起舞，引起了老同志们','172.16.100.2','172.16.100.2','1644980602','<p style=\"margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\'Calibri\',\'sans-serif\';text-align:left;text-indent:29.0pt\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size:14.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:black\">在传统的元宵佳节来临之际，为营造欢乐祥和的节日气氛，进一步丰富老同志的精神文化生活，<span>2022</span>年<span>2</span>月<span>14</span>日，盐城市第一人民医院离退休干部处举办了<span>“</span>迎元宵 猜灯谜<span>”</span>活动，吸引了不少老同志前来参与。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; text-align: center; text-indent: 24pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体\"><img width=\"246\" height=\"310\" src=\"/ewebeditor/uploadfile/image/2022/02/16/20220216110050997001.jpg\" align=\"center\"></span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体\">&nbsp;<img width=\"239\" height=\"311\" src=\"/ewebeditor/uploadfile/image/2022/02/16/20220216110050142002.png\" align=\"center\"></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\'Calibri\',\'sans-serif\';margin-top:0cm;margin-right:4.2pt;\r\nmargin-bottom:0cm;margin-left:4.2pt;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:left\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体\"><img width=\"32\" height=\"32\" src=\"/ewebeditor/uploadfile/image/2022/02/16/20220216110051987003.png\" alt=\"图片\"></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; margin: 0cm 4.2pt 0.0001pt; text-align: left; text-indent: 29pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:14.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:black\">活动现场张灯结彩，<span>200</span>多条挂在彩带上的谜面随风起舞，引起了老同志们浓厚的兴趣。灯谜内容内容丰富，幽默诙谐，在一条条鲜艳的谜语前，一双双欣喜而激动的眼睛闪烁着智慧的光芒，他们聚精会神地看着一个个灯谜，认真琢磨，绞尽脑汁，时而凝思苦想、时而相互交流，你一言、我一语，互相提示和讨论，享受着传统的民俗之乐。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; margin: 0cm 4.2pt 0.0001pt; text-align: center; text-indent: 29pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\"><span style=\"font-size: 19.3333px;\"><br>\r\n</span>\r\n</span><span style=\"font-size: 14.5pt; font-family: 宋体; color: black;\"><img width=\"268\" height=\"352\" src=\"/ewebeditor/uploadfile/image/2022/02/16/20220216110051554004.png\" align=\"center\"></span><span style=\"font-size: 14.5pt; font-family: 宋体; color: black;\">&nbsp;<img width=\"254\" height=\"352\" src=\"/ewebeditor/uploadfile/image/2022/02/16/20220216110051267005.png\" align=\"center\"></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\'Calibri\',\'sans-serif\';text-align:left\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\'Calibri\',\'sans-serif\';margin-top:0cm;margin-right:4.2pt;\r\nmargin-bottom:0cm;margin-left:4.2pt;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:left\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体\"><img width=\"32\" height=\"32\" src=\"/ewebeditor/uploadfile/image/2022/02/16/20220216110051987003.png\" alt=\"图片\"></span><span style=\"font-size:14.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:black\">很快一条条谜语就被确认答案的志愿者取下，兑奖处排起了长队，有的老同志提着奖品开心的向旁边的朋友炫耀着，<span>“</span>看我猜谜中的奖品<span>”</span>那个高兴与得意劲，看得旁人也着急，整个活动现场到处都充满了欢声笑语，洋溢着祥和喜庆的气氛。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体\">&nbsp; <img width=\"260\" height=\"235\" src=\"/ewebeditor/uploadfile/image/2022/02/16/20220216110051854006.png\" align=\"center\">&nbsp;<img width=\"264\" height=\"243\" src=\"/ewebeditor/uploadfile/image/2022/02/16/20220216110051955007.jpg\" align=\"center\"></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\'Calibri\',\'sans-serif\';margin-top:0cm;margin-right:4.2pt;\r\nmargin-bottom:0cm;margin-left:4.2pt;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:left\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体\"><img width=\"32\" height=\"32\" src=\"/ewebeditor/uploadfile/image/2022/02/16/20220216110051987003.png\" alt=\"图片\"></span><span style=\"font-size:14.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:black\">此次迎元宵猜灯谜活动的开展，不仅增添了节日的喜庆气氛，为大家带来了欢乐，更让大家充分感受到了中国传统文化的魅力。</span></p>','','','','','');
