\"\">1.2</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\"Times New Roman\";\r\nmso-hansi-font-family:\"Times New Roman\"\">招标内容：</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\"Times New Roman\",\"serif\"\">6</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\"Times New Roman\";\r\nmso-hansi-font-family:\"Times New Roman\"\">号楼</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\"Times New Roman\",\"serif\"\">1</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\"Times New Roman\";\r\nmso-hansi-font-family:\"Times New Roman\"\">楼介入中心门口等处中央空调管道维修更换等项目，具体内容详见招标人提供的工程量清单。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\"Times New Roman\",\"serif\"\"></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:24.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:21.0pt;mso-line-height-rule:exactly\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\"Times New Roman\",\"serif\"\">1.3</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\"Times New Roman\";\r\nmso-hansi-font-family:\"Times New Roman\"\">项目地点：<span style=\"background:white\">盐城市第一人民医院北区（毓龙西路</span></span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\"Times New Roman\",\"serif\";\r\nbackground:white\">166</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体;\r\nmso-ascii-font-family:\"Times New Roman\";mso-hansi-font-family:\"Times New Roman\";\r\nbackground:white\">号）</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\r\n\"Times New Roman\",\"serif\"\"></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:24.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:21.0pt;mso-line-height-rule:exactly;tab-stops:45.0pt\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\"Times New Roman\",\"serif\"\">1.4</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\"Times New Roman\";\r\nmso-hansi-font-family:\"Times New Roman\"\">工期要求：</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\"Times New Roman\",\"serif\"\"> 15 </span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\"Times New Roman\";\r\nmso-hansi-font-family:\"Times New Roman\"\">日历天，具体开工日期以招标人的通知为准。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\"Times New Roman\",\"serif\"\"></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:24.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:21.0pt;mso-line-height-rule:exactly;tab-stops:45.0pt\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\"Times New Roman\",\"serif\"\">1.5</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\"Times New Roman\";\r\nmso-hansi-font-family:\"Times New Roman\"\">质量要求：符合国家及行业规范</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\"Times New Roman\",\"serif\"\">“</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\"Times New Roman\";\r\nmso-hansi-font-family:\"Times New Roman\"\">合格</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\"Times New Roman\",\"serif\"\">”</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\"Times New Roman\";\r\nmso-hansi-font-family:\"Times New Roman\"\">标准，</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;\r\nfont-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\"Times New Roman\";mso-hansi-font-family:\r\nCalibri\">确保中央空调正常运行。</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体;\r\nmso-ascii-font-family:\"Times New Roman\";mso-hansi-font-family:\"Times New Roman\"\">质保期</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\"Times New Roman\",\"serif\"\">1</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\"Times New Roman\";\r\nmso-hansi-font-family:\"Times New Roman\"\">年。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\"Times New Roman\",\"serif\"\"></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:24.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:21.0pt;mso-line-height-rule:exactly;tab-stops:45.0pt\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\"Times New Roman\",\"serif\"\">1.6</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\"Times New Roman\";\r\nmso-hansi-font-family:\"Times New Roman\"\">发包方式：包工包料。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\"Times New Roman\",\"serif\"\"></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:24.1pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:21.0pt;mso-line-height-rule:exactly;layout-grid-mode:char\"><b style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight:normal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">2</span></b><b style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight:normal\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri\">、投标人应当具备的主要资格条件</span></b><b style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight:normal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"></span></b></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:24.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:21.0pt;mso-line-height-rule:exactly;layout-grid-mode:char\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri\">投标人须是具有建设行政主管部门核发的建筑机电安装工程专业承包二级及以上资质的独立法人，并具有有效的安全生产许证。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:24.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:21.0pt;mso-line-height-rule:exactly;mso-pagination:widow-orphan\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\"Times New Roman\",\"serif\";\r\nmso-font-kerning:0pt\">3</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体;\r\nmso-ascii-font-family:\"Times New Roman\";mso-hansi-font-family:\"Times New Roman\";\r\nmso-font-kerning:0pt\">、投标报名及招标文件的获取</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:\r\n12.0pt;font-family:\"Times New Roman\",\"serif\";mso-font-kerning:0pt\"></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:24.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:21.0pt;mso-line-height-rule:exactly;mso-pagination:widow-orphan\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\"Times New Roman\";\r\nmso-hansi-font-family:\"Times New Roman\";mso-font-kerning:0pt\">请符合上述资质条件的投标人携带单位介绍信（或授权委托书，须注明联系人、电话及邮箱）原件到江苏全盛工程造价事务所有限公司（盐城市解放南路</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\"Times New Roman\",\"serif\";\r\nmso-font-kerning:0pt\">199</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体;\r\nmso-ascii-font-family:\"Times New Roman\";mso-hansi-font-family:\"Times New Roman\";\r\nmso-font-kerning:0pt\">号阳光大厦</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;\r\nfont-family:\"Times New Roman\",\"serif\";mso-font-kerning:0pt\">B</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\"Times New Roman\";\r\nmso-hansi-font-family:\"Times New Roman\";mso-font-kerning:0pt\">座四楼）投标报名，投标报名时间</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\"Times New Roman\",\"serif\";\r\nmso-font-kerning:0pt\">2022</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\"Times New Roman\";mso-hansi-font-family:\"Times New Roman\";\r\nmso-font-kerning:0pt\">年</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;\r\nfont-family:\"Times New Roman\",\"serif\";mso-font-kerning:0pt\">3</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\"Times New Roman\";\r\nmso-hansi-font-family:\"Times New Roman\";mso-font-kerning:0pt\">月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\"Times New Roman\",\"serif\";\r\nmso-font-kerning:0pt\">28</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体;\r\nmso-ascii-font-family:\"Times New Roman\";mso-hansi-font-family:\"Times New Roman\";\r\nmso-font-kerning:0pt\">日</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;\r\nfont-family:\"Times New Roman\",\"serif\";mso-font-kerning:0pt\">8</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\"Times New Roman\";\r\nmso-hansi-font-family:\"Times New Roman\";mso-font-kerning:0pt\">时至</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\"Times New Roman\",\"serif\";\r\nmso-font-kerning:0pt\">2022</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\"Times New Roman\";mso-hansi-font-family:\"Times New Roman\";\r\nmso-font-kerning:0pt\">年</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;\r\nfont-family:\"Times New Roman\",\"serif\";mso-font-kerning:0pt\">4</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\"Times New Roman\";\r\nmso-hansi-font-family:\"Times New Roman\";mso-font-kerning:0pt\">月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\"Times New Roman\",\"serif\";\r\nmso-font-kerning:0pt\">1</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体;\r\nmso-ascii-font-family:\"Times New Roman\";mso-hansi-font-family:\"Times New Roman\";\r\nmso-font-kerning:0pt\">日</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;\r\nfont-family:\"Times New Roman\",\"serif\";mso-font-kerning:0pt\">18</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\"Times New Roman\";\r\nmso-hansi-font-family:\"Times New Roman\";mso-font-kerning:0pt\">时。联系人：祁建峰；手机：</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\"Times New Roman\",\"serif\";\r\nmso-font-kerning:0pt\">13626206678</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;\r\nfont-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\"Times New Roman\";mso-hansi-font-family:\r\n\"Times New Roman\";mso-font-kerning:0pt\">。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\"Times New Roman\",\"serif\";mso-font-kerning:\r\n0pt\"></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:24.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:21.0pt;mso-line-height-rule:exactly;mso-pagination:widow-orphan\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\"Times New Roman\",\"serif\";\r\nmso-font-kerning:0pt\">4</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体;\r\nmso-ascii-font-family:\"Times New Roman\";mso-hansi-font-family:\"Times New Roman\";\r\nmso-font-kerning:0pt\">、本项目评标办法采用</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;\r\nfont-family:\"Times New Roman\",\"serif\";mso-font-kerning:0pt\">“</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\"Times New Roman\";\r\nmso-hansi-font-family:\"Times New Roman\";mso-font-kerning:0pt\">合理低价法</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\"Times New Roman\",\"serif\";\r\nmso-font-kerning:0pt\">”</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体;\r\nmso-ascii-font-family:\"Times New Roman\";mso-hansi-font-family:\"Times New Roman\";\r\nmso-font-kerning:0pt\">。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;\r\nfont-family:\"Times New Roman\",\"serif\";mso-font-kerning:0pt\"></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:24.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:21.0pt;mso-line-height-rule:exactly;mso-pagination:widow-orphan\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\"Times New Roman\",\"serif\";\r\nmso-font-kerning:0pt\">5</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体;\r\nmso-ascii-font-family:\"Times New Roman\";mso-hansi-font-family:\"Times New Roman\";\r\nmso-font-kerning:0pt\">、投标申请人有违反《盐城市市场廉政准则规定（试行）》中规定情形的，招标人将拒绝投标报名。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\"Times New Roman\",\"serif\";\r\nmso-font-kerning:0pt\"></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:24.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:21.0pt;mso-line-height-rule:exactly;mso-pagination:widow-orphan\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\"Times New Roman\",\"serif\";\r\nmso-font-kerning:0pt\">6</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体;\r\nmso-ascii-font-family:\"Times New Roman\";mso-hansi-font-family:\"Times New Roman\";\r\nmso-font-kerning:0pt\">、招投标监督管理机构及投诉电话：盐城市第一人民医院监督审查室，联系电话</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\"Times New Roman\",\"serif\";\r\nmso-font-kerning:0pt\">0515-66696810</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;\r\nfont-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\"Times New Roman\";mso-hansi-font-family:\r\n\"Times New Roman\";mso-font-kerning:0pt\">。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\"Times New Roman\",\"serif\";mso-font-kerning:\r\n0pt\"></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:24.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:21.0pt;mso-line-height-rule:exactly;mso-pagination:widow-orphan\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\"Times New Roman\";\r\nmso-hansi-font-family:\"Times New Roman\";mso-font-kerning:0pt\">其余内容详见招标文件。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\"Times New Roman\",\"serif\";\r\nmso-font-kerning:0pt\"></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:24.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:21.0pt;mso-line-height-rule:exactly;mso-pagination:widow-orphan\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\"Times New Roman\",\"serif\";\r\nmso-font-kerning:0pt\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent: 144pt; line-height: 21pt; text-align: right;\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\"Times New Roman\";\r\nmso-hansi-font-family:\"Times New Roman\";mso-font-kerning:0pt\">招标人：盐城市第一人民医院</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\"Times New Roman\",\"serif\";\r\nmso-font-kerning:0pt\"></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent: 144pt; line-height: 21pt; text-align: right;\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\"Times New Roman\";\r\nmso-hansi-font-family:\"Times New Roman\";mso-font-kerning:0pt\">时间：</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\"Times New Roman\",\"serif\";\r\nmso-font-kerning:0pt\">2022</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\r\n宋体;