#333333\">按要求填写《盐城市第一人民医院设备报价表》（见附件）。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-right:0cm;margin-left:0cm;font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\'Calibri\',\'sans-serif\';margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:30.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;color:#333333\">6.</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;color:#333333\">报名截止时间：<span>2022</span>年<span>04</span>月<span>24</span>日<span>24</span>：<span>00</span></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-right:0cm;margin-left:0cm;font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\'Calibri\',\'sans-serif\';margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:10.0pt;margin-left:0cm;layout-grid-mode:char;font-size:11.0pt;font-family:\'Tahoma\',\'sans-serif\';line-height:30.0pt\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;\r\nfont-family:宋体;color:#333333\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;联系人：李老师<span>&nbsp; </span>联系方式：<span>0515-88508946&nbsp; QQ:651830413(</span>推荐<span>)</span></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-right:0cm;margin-left:0cm;font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\'Calibri\',\'sans-serif\';margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:10.0pt;margin-left:0cm;layout-grid-mode:char;font-size:11.0pt;font-family:\'Tahoma\',\'sans-serif\';line-height:30.0pt\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;\r\nfont-family:宋体;color:#333333\"><span><br>\r\n</span></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-right:0cm;margin-left:0cm;font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\'Calibri\',\'sans-serif\';margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:10.0pt;margin-left:0cm;layout-grid-mode:char;font-size:11.0pt;font-family:\'Tahoma\',\'sans-serif\';line-height:30.0pt\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;<img border=\"0\" src=\"/ewebeditor/sysimage/icon16/doc.gif\" style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt;\"><a href=\"/ewebeditor/uploadfile/file/2022/04/18/20220418152405981.docx\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt;\">附件：盐城市第一人民医院设备报价表.docx</a></p>','','','','','');
INSERT INTO `p8_cms_item_article_addon` VALUES ('2425','3248','1','','','盐城市第一人民医院疫情防控指挥中心装修工程已具备招标条件，项目所需资金来源为自筹资金并已落实。现通过公开招标方式邀请潜在投标人参加本项目的投标报名。现就有关事项公告如下：一、江苏双清工程造价咨询有限公司受招标人委托具体负责本项目的招标事宜。二、符合本','172.16.100.2','172.16.100.2','1650268279','<p style=\"margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\'Times New Roman\',\'serif\';text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:23.0pt\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体\">盐城市第一人民医院疫情防控指挥中心装修工程已具备招标条件，项目所需资金来源为自筹资金并已落实。现通过公开招标方式邀请潜在投标人参加本项目的投标报名。现就有关事项公告如下：</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\'Times New Roman\',\'serif\';text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:23.0pt\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体\">一、江苏双清工程造价咨询有限公司受招标人委托具体负责本项目的招标事宜。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\'Times New Roman\',\'serif\';text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:23.0pt\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体\">二、符合本项目招标公告资格要求的投标的申请人均可参加该项目投标。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\'Times New Roman\',\'serif\';text-indent:24.1pt;line-height:23.0pt\"><b><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体\">三、项目概况：</span></b></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\'Times New Roman\',\'serif\';text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:23.0pt\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体\">1</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体\">、工程名称：盐城市第一人民医院疫情防控指挥中心装修工程。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\'Times New Roman\',\'serif\';text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:23.0pt\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体\">2</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体\">、工程地点：盐城市第一人民医院主院区（<span style=\"color:black\">人民南路<span>66</span>号</span>）。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\'Times New Roman\',\'serif\';text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:23.0pt\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体\">3</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体\">、招标规模：工程造价约<span>52.44</span>万元。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\'Times New Roman\',\'serif\';text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:22.0pt\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体\">4</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体\">、招标范围及内容：盐城市第一人民医院疫情防控指挥中心装修工程的施工，具体内容详见招标人提供的图纸及工程量清单。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\'Times New Roman\',\'serif\';text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:23.0pt\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体\">5</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体\">、工期要求：<span>20</span>日历天，具体开工日期以招标人的通知为准。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\'Times New Roman\',\'serif\';text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:23.0pt\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体\">6</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体\">、质量标准：符合国家“合格”标准，质保期<span>2</span>年。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\'Times New Roman\',\'serif\';text-indent:24.1pt;line-height:23.0pt\"><b><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体\">四、投标人资格要求：</span></b></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\'Times New Roman\',\'serif\';text-align:left;text-indent:24.0pt;\r\nline-height:22.0pt;layout-grid-mode:char\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size:\r\n12.0pt;font-family:宋体\">1</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体\">、投标人须具有有效的建筑装修装饰工程专业承包二级及以上施工资质的独立法人，并具有有效的安全生产许可证。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\'Times New Roman\',\'serif\';text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:23.0pt\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体\">2</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体\">、项目负责人资格类别和等级<span>:</span>项目负责人须具有建筑工程专业二级及以上建造师资格（投标时须提供建造师注册证书）和安全生产考核合格证（<span>B</span>类）。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\'Times New Roman\',\'serif\';text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:23.0pt\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体\">3</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体\">、本次招标不接受联合体投标。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\'Times New Roman\',\'serif\';text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:23.0pt\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体\">4</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体\">、财务要求：投标人应具有独立订立合同的能力，未处于财产被接管、冻结和破产状态。<span>&nbsp;</span></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\'Times New Roman\',\'serif\';text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:23.0pt\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体\">5</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体\">、信誉要求：投标人没有被国家、江苏省省级有关部门及盐城市级有关部门暂停招投标或市场准入资格且在公示处罚期内。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\'Times New Roman\',\'serif\';text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:23.0pt\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体\">6</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体\">、投标申请人须保证委托代理人、项目负责人均为本单位的正式职工，并确保从投标截止之日当月向前连续<span>6</span>个月均已在本单位缴纳养老保险（例：如开标日期为<span>2020</span>年<span>7</span>月的某一天，则投标单位需保证以上人员<span>2020</span>年<span>1-6</span>月养老保险均在本单位缴纳）。投标时无须提供证明材料，如有质疑或招标人要求，再按要求提供相关证明材料。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\'Times New Roman\',\'serif\';text-indent:24.1pt;line-height:23.0pt\"><b><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体\">五、招标文件获取：</span></b></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\'Times New Roman\',\'serif\';text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:23.0pt\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体\">请有意参与投标的申请人将单位介绍信或委托书（自行注明联系方式及邮箱）原件扫描件于<b><span>2022</span>年<span>4</span>月<span>23</span>日<span>12:00</span>时</b>前发送到<span>806404021@qq.com</span>邮箱进行报名，报名费跟财务联系，财务电话<span>0515-88200706</span>，<span>13515130964</span>，逾期不再受理。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\'Times New Roman\',\'serif\';text-indent:24.1pt;line-height:23.0pt\"><b><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体\">六、投标保证金</span></b></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\'Times New Roman\',\'serif\';text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:23.0pt\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体\">本项目投标保证金为人民币<span>8000</span>元，具体详见招标文件。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\'Times New Roman\',\'serif\';text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:23.0pt\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体\">七、本项目资格审查办法采用<b>资格后审</b>；评标办法采用<b>综合评估法</b>，具体详见招标文件。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\'Times New Roman\',\'serif\';text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:23.0pt\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体\">八、本项目严禁挂靠，一经核实挂靠，将被取消投标、中标资格，并按相关规定进行处罚，直至建议有关部门吊销资质证书。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\'Times New Roman\',\'serif\';text-indent:24.1pt;line-height:23.0pt\"><b><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体\">九、特别提醒：</span></b></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\'Times New Roman\',\'serif\';text-indent:24.1pt;line-height:23.0pt\"><b><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体\">本项目采用不见面开标（腾讯会议），开标当日，投标人无需到达开标现场，投标人可以在开标前下载“腾讯会议”直播<span>APP</span>，在任意地点通过<span> PC</span>端或移动端的“腾讯会议”及具有视频功能相应的配套硬件设备</span></b><b><span style=\"font-family:宋体;background:white\">上观看直播和在线交流。</span></b></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\'Times New Roman\',\'serif\';text-indent:24.1pt;line-height:23.0pt\"><b><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体\">十、联系方式</span></b></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\'Times New Roman\',\'serif\';text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:23.0pt\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体\">招标人：盐城市第一人民医院</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\'Times New Roman\',\'serif\';text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:23.0pt\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体\">地<span>&nbsp; </span>址<span style=\"color:black\">：人民南路<span>66</span>号</span></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\'Times New Roman\',\'serif\';text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:23.0pt\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体;color:black\">联系人：沈剑</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\'Times New Roman\',\'serif\';text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:23.0pt\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体;color:black\">电<span>&nbsp; </span>话：<span>19905</span></span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;\r\nfont-family:宋体\">100321</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\'Times New Roman\',\'serif\';text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:23.0pt\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体\">招标代理机构：江苏双清工程造价咨询有限公司<span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\'Times New Roman\',\'serif\';text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:23.0pt\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体\">地<span>&nbsp; </span>址：盐城市紫薇广场<span>C</span>区<span>7</span>楼<span>&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\'Times New Roman\',\'serif\';text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:23.0pt\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体\">联系人：尤鸿望、张旭良<span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\'Times New Roman\',\'serif\';text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:23.0pt\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体\">电<span>&nbsp; </span>话：<span>0515-88200316</span>、<span>13515130964</span></span></p>','','','','','');
INSERT INTO `p8_cms_item_article_addon` VALUES ('2426','3249','1','','/ewebeditor/uploadfile/image/2022/04/19/20220419143057506_s.jpg','拾金不昧是中华民族的传统美德，也是高尚品德的表现。4月17日，盐城市第一人民医院物管办保洁员陈琴用实际行动诠释了诚信之美，平凡举动不仅温暖人心，也展现了平凡岗位不平凡的品质！当天下午，陈琴在北院区消化内科二病区和往常一样打扫卫生，打扫厕所时发现，厕所门','172.16.100.2','172.16.100.2','1650349874','<p style=\"margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\'Calibri\',\'sans-serif\';text-indent:28.0pt\"><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;\r\nfont-family:仿宋,仿宋_GB2312\">拾金不昧是中华民族的传统美德，也是高尚品德的表现。<span>4</span>月<span>17</span>日，盐城市第一人民医院物管办保洁员陈琴用实际行动诠释了诚信之美，平凡举动不仅温暖人心，也展现了平凡岗位不平凡的品质！</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\'Calibri\',\'sans-serif\';text-indent:28.0pt\"><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;\r\nfont-family:仿宋,仿宋_GB2312\">当天下午，陈琴在北院区消化内科二病区和往常一样打扫卫生，打扫厕所时发现，厕所门上挂了一个黑色皮包。陈琴等待了十几分钟发现无人认领，于是她将黑色皮包送至护士站吧台告知当班护士。<span>20</span>分钟后一个满头大汗的老奶奶奔至病房询问是否有人拾到一个包。当班护士核对信息后将包交给老奶奶。据了解，老人的丈夫在重症监护室抢救，因焦急把包遗忘在门上，包内有一万多现金，是家人的救命钱。皮包失而复得，老人十分激动，面对感激万分的患者家属，保洁员陈琴却说：“捡到东西还给失主是我应该做的，当时想到丢包人一定非常着急，就赶紧把包送至护士站。”</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\'Calibri\',\'sans-serif\'\"><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;font-family:仿宋,仿宋_GB2312\">弘扬传统美德，践行文明新风。陈琴是市一院众多拾金不昧职工中的一员。他们用自己的实际行动展现了中华传统美德，搭起了医患之间温暖的连心桥，传递着和谐美好的社会正能量。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\'Calibri\',\'sans-serif\'\"><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;font-family:仿宋,仿宋_GB2312\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;<a href=\"/ewebeditor/uploadfile/image/2022/04/19/20220419143057506.jpg\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"/ewebeditor/uploadfile/image/2022/04/19/20220419143057506_s.jpg\" border=\"0\"></a><br>\r\n</span></p>','','','','','');
