e-height:1.5;\r\nfont-family:宋体\">3.</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:1.5;\r\nfont-family:宋体\">邮编：<span>224006&nbsp; </span></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\'Calibri\',\'sans-serif\';margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\'Calibri\',\'sans-serif\';text-align:left;text-indent:24.0pt;\r\nline-height:1.5\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:1.5;font-family:\r\n宋体\">电话：<span>0515</span>—<span>88508915</span></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\'Calibri\',\'sans-serif\';margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\'Calibri\',\'sans-serif\';text-align:left;text-indent:24.0pt;\r\nline-height:1.5\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:1.5;font-family:\r\n宋体\">联系人：刘国霞</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\'Calibri\',\'sans-serif\';margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\'Calibri\',\'sans-serif\';text-align:left;text-indent:24.0pt;\r\nline-height:1.5\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:1.5;\r\nfont-family:宋体\">4.</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:1.5;\r\nfont-family:宋体\">审核：医院根据报名材料对报名人员资格进行审核，社会化学员招收结合本院培训基地招生要求发布进入考核人员名单。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\'Calibri\',\'sans-serif\';margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\'Calibri\',\'sans-serif\';text-align:left;text-indent:24.0pt;\r\nline-height:1.5\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:1.5;font-family:\r\n宋体\">社会化学员报名现场资格审核需携带下列材料：</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\'Calibri\',\'sans-serif\';margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\'Calibri\',\'sans-serif\';text-align:left;text-indent:24.0pt;\r\nline-height:1.5\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:1.5;font-family:\r\n宋体\">①</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:1.5;font-family:宋体\">简历一份。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\'Calibri\',\'sans-serif\';margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\'Calibri\',\'sans-serif\';text-align:left;text-indent:24.0pt;\r\nline-height:1.5\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:1.5;font-family:\r\n宋体\">②</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:1.5;font-family:宋体\">身份证原件及复印件一份。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\'Calibri\',\'sans-serif\';margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\'Calibri\',\'sans-serif\';text-align:left;text-indent:24.0pt;\r\nline-height:1.5\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:1.5;font-family:\r\n宋体\">③</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:1.5;font-family:宋体\">近期正面免冠二寸照片</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:1.5;font-family:\'Verdana\',\'sans-serif\'\">2</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:1.5;font-family:宋体\">张。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\'Calibri\',\'sans-serif\';margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\'Calibri\',\'sans-serif\';text-align:left;text-indent:24.0pt;\r\nline-height:1.5\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:1.5;font-family:\r\n宋体\">④</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:1.5;font-family:宋体\">毕业证书及学位证书原件及复印件一份。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\'Calibri\',\'sans-serif\';margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\'Calibri\',\'sans-serif\';text-align:left;text-indent:24.0pt;\r\nline-height:1.5\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:1.5;font-family:\r\n宋体\">⑤</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:1.5;font-family:宋体\">英语、计算机等级考试合格证书原件及复印件一份。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\'Calibri\',\'sans-serif\';margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\'Calibri\',\'sans-serif\';text-align:left;text-indent:24.0pt;\r\nline-height:1.5\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:1.5;font-family:\r\n宋体\">⑥</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:1.5;font-family:宋体\">获奖证书原件及复印件一份</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\'Calibri\',\'sans-serif\';margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\'Calibri\',\'sans-serif\';margin-left:18.65pt;text-align:left;\r\ntext-indent:24.1pt;line-height:1.5\" align=\"left\"><b><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;\r\nline-height:1.5;font-family:\'Verdana\',\'sans-serif\'\">七、</span></b><b><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:1.5;font-family:宋体\">考试</span></b></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\'Calibri\',\'sans-serif\';margin-top:7.5pt;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:7.5pt;margin-left:\r\n0cm;text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:1.5;background:white\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;color:#151515;background:white\">考试方式分笔试、技能考核和面试，内容侧重于临床专业知识、基本技能和综合素质测试。社会化学员考试具体时间和地点另行通知，免收考试费。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\'Calibri\',\'sans-serif\';margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\'Calibri\',\'sans-serif\';margin-left:18.65pt;text-align:left;\r\ntext-indent:24.1pt;line-height:1.5\" align=\"left\"><b><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;\r\nline-height:1.5;font-family:\'Verdana\',\'sans-serif\'\">八、</span></b><b><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:1.5;font-family:宋体\">体检及录取</span></b></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\'Calibri\',\'sans-serif\';margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\'Calibri\',\'sans-serif\';text-align:left;text-indent:24.0pt;\r\nline-height:1.5\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:1.5;font-family:\r\n宋体\">根据考试总成绩，从高分到低分按招收人数</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;\r\nline-height:1.5;font-family:\'Verdana\',\'sans-serif\'\">1</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:1.5;font-family:宋体\">∶</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:1.5;font-family:\'Verdana\',\'sans-serif\'\">1</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:1.5;font-family:宋体\">确定体检人员，体检标准参照《国家公务员录用体检通用标准（试行）》。对体检合格录取人员，按照相关规定签订培训协议，办理有关手续。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\'Calibri\',\'sans-serif\';margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\'Calibri\',\'sans-serif\';margin-left:18.65pt;text-align:left;\r\ntext-indent:24.0pt;line-height:1.5\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;\r\nline-height:1.5;font-family:宋体\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<img border=\"0\" src=\"/ewebeditor/sysimage/icon16/xls.gif\"><a href=\"/ewebeditor/uploadfile/file/2022/05/16/20220516163526443.xls\" target=\"_blank\">个人简历.xls</a>','','','','','');
